{"type": "article", "id": 23281, "title": "彩色蜡烛包装", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-04T07:30:20Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160607174306WHJ5jwvilKhrTVg9.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">当你不知道送什么礼物给别人时，蜡烛也许是个不错的选择。这组蜡烛采用立方体盒子式的包装，盖子下面露出了里面盒子的彩色的边，是不完全遮盖的，有点引人揭开它的感觉。彩色的边对应了里面放蜡烛的杯子的颜色，对比带有简单文字的白色“外罩”，显得更纯粹。盒子上的文字是居中排布，而普兰、桃红和墨绿这三种选色都很清新淡雅。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174302BDodQ7R08yJ6HI2Z.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.5\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174303FpBv9hlDmgnLZzJV.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201606071743044tBovsAYOhr2mDQM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174304VyzGtePE1MXLnhCs.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174304Kuhcx8ZR7v9LMqsX.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160607174306ARVHJx1jqQwInW8c.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}